      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed thanks to a refreshed suspension with poly-bushings and a verified rear subframe reinforcement. Mechanically sound with a recent Vanos overhaul and valve adjustment, this M3 utilizes its factory limited-slip differential to provide exceptional turn-in and corner-exit traction. It\u2019s a high-revving, analog machine ready for the canyons.",
